    "body": "> In addition the popup message is confusing \"...Status > Face ID...\". Where shall I enable it, shall I enable \"Lock app with face ID\" option too if this is the first log in?\r\n\r\nTo enable authentication without a password you need to click on 'Cancel' in the popup and then log in with the password.\r\nThen after relaunching the app, it will not require a password anymore for login.\r\n\r\n> It is disabled and never used but the popup continues\r\n\r\nIf you log out from profile, even if you checked \"Save password\" , you need to login again.\r\nI'm not sure what are your expectations from \"Save password\" functionality if you enable it\r\n",
